The paper deals with capacity analysis of multiple-antenna systems affected by phase noise, which is a topic related to information theory (cs.IT) and communication systems (cs.COMM). The use of a common oscillator setup and deterministic channel matrix also suggests a systems and control theory perspective (cs.SY). The specific application of microwave backhaul links falls under the category of mobile and wireless networking (cs.MM) and network infrastructure (cs.NI).
